#based on:
#https://github.com/php-fig/fig-standards/blob/master/accepted/PSR-2-coding-style-guide.md
code must follow psr-1
code must use 4 spaces instead of tabs
lines should be soft limited to 120 characters
lines should be limited to 80 characters
one blank line after namespace
one blank line after last use
opening braces for classes must go on the next line
closing braces must for classes go on the next line
opening braces for methods must go on the next line
closing braces must for methods go on the next line
visibiliy must be declared on all properties and methods
abstract and final must be declared before visibility
control structure keywords must have one space after them, method- and functioncalls must not
opening parentheses for control structures must not have spaces after or before them
